DSpace upgrade checklist:
Add config changes
Finalize look and feel
Disable authentication options in production config or disable e-person aspect in xmlui.xconf and restart Tomcat
git archive 1.7.1 branch src code to /websys/src/dspace
git archive 1.6.1 dspace.cfg to /websys/install/dspace
check permissions on everything (webservd)
snapshot database, copy assetstore
as dspace, run 1.5.2-1.6.x database upgrade scripts against db copy
remove 1.6.1 dspace.cfg
double-check 1.7.1 dspace.cfg
as dspace, run 1.6.x-1.7.x upgrade scripts against db and assetstore copies
rebuild search
import logs
mvn, ant build to /websys/install
deploy webapps
configure Tomcat 6 server.xml for port 80